## Fixtures (Test Data)

Fixtures provide test data.

```yaml
# test/fixtures/users.yml

john:
  email: john@example.com
  password_digest: <%= BCrypt::Password.create('password') %>
  first_name: John
  last_name: Doe
  admin: false

jane:
  email: jane@example.com
  password_digest: <%= BCrypt::Password.create('password') %>
  first_name: Jane
  last_name: Smith
  admin: true
```

```yaml
# test/fixtures/articles.yml

one:
  user: john
  title: First Article
  body: This is the first article body
  status: published
  published_at: <%= 1.day.ago %>

two:
  user: jane
  title: Second Article
  body: This is the second article body
  status: draft
```

**Usage in tests:**
```ruby
test "user has many articles" do
  user = users(:john)
  assert_equal 1, user.articles.count
end
```

